main event: Two round white objects the size of a quarter were seen at 30 degree elevation, observed for 8 minutes, and then disappeared at the same elevation. The objects split and disappeared into the horizon after being visually seen for 7 minutes.
interesting points: Objects were observed at a specific 30 degree elevation and disappeared at the same elevation.
They split and disappeared into the horizon after 7 minutes of visual observation.
The report was from a civilian source, an electrical engineer and a housewife in Dallas, Texas.
There were no photographs included in the report.
Insufficient data for evaluation was concluded by the investigators.
